  "subject": "ONLY REVIEW NO MERGE",
  "commit_message": "ONLY REVIEW NO MERGE\n\nThis patch is only for review, NO MERGE\n\nDraft of new Prolog Filter.\n\n* Reject multiple files if one is INFO.yaml\n* Reject approval if Jenkins has not approved INFO.yaml\n* Allow self approval if Jenkins User\n\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/sandbox-3/+/109283 1 INFO.yaml\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/sandbox-3/+/109280 1 INFO.yaml and 1 extra file\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/sandbox-3/+/109396 Multiple files, no INFO.yaml\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/sandbox-3/+/109397 1 file, no INFO.yaml\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/sandbox-3/+/109992 Faulty INFO file\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nSigned-off-by: Bengt Thuree <bthuree@linuxfoundation.org>\nChange-Id: I06e4de4c49690fd1156bc8b6bf431b7c75e74a03\n",
